item.title: EP 128 - Operation Highjump: The US vs Nazi UFOs!
item.itunes:title: Operation High Jump: The US vs Nazi UFOs!
item.description:
For the first time in world history, a hitchhiking story involving shovels and a graveyard that doesn't end how you would expect. A shop purports to sell pieces of the Betz Sphere. And then we take a look at the fact, and fiction, of Operation Highjump. Did the US fight UFO Nazis in Antarctica?
